  "solution": {
    "outline": [
      "令 A=∫0^1 f(t)dt，将其视为常数",
      "x=0 得到 f(0)=4A",
      "对原式求导得到一阶线性微分方程",
      "代回 A 条件解出常数 C"
    ],
    "steps": [
      {
        "idx": 1,
        "description": "令 A=∫0^1 f(t)dt。代入 x=0：f(0)=4A。",
        "math": "f(0)=4\\int_0^1 f(t)dt"
      },
      {
        "idx": 2,
        "description": "对①两边对 x 求导：左侧 f'(x)，右侧为 3+3f(x)。",
        "math": "f'(x)=3+3f(x)=3(1+f(x))"
      },
      {
        "idx": 3,
        "description": "化为 (1+f)'/(1+f)=3，积分得 1+f(x)=Ce^{3x}，即 f(x)=Ce^{3x}-1。",
        "math": "f(x)=Ce^{3x}-1"
      },
      {
        "idx": 4,
        "description": "用 f(0)=4A：C-1=4(∫0^1(Ce^{3t}-1)dt)。计算积分并解出 C=9/(4e^3-7)。",
        "math": "C=\\frac{9}{4e^3-7}"
      }
    ],
